 《博德之门 3》在 30GB 更新中获得新的尾声和新的难度模式https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-gets-new-epilogue-and-new-difficulty-modes-in-30gb-update-3551420?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign= baldus-gate-3-在 30gb 更新中获取新尾声和新难度模式Ryan EasbyThu, 30 Nov 2023 16:48:32 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCPS5Video Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3551420 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是一个巨大的下载</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-gets-new-epilogue-and-new-difficulty-modes-in-30gb-update-3551420">《博德之门 3》的新结局和新难度模式在 30GB 更新中</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-launch-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii">《博德之门 3》</a></em>已收到第五个补丁，修复了众多问题，并在一次大小为 30GB 的更新中为游戏添加了新内容。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/boss-level-2023-amelia-tyler-baldurs-gate-3-3550385">《博德之门 3》如何让叙述者阿米莉亚·泰勒度过“非常黑暗的时期”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该补丁包含一个新的尾声，增加了近 4,000 行额外的对话，让你可以告别在整个大型角色扮演游戏中与你结下不解之缘的角色。</p><p>除此之外，更新还增加了两种新的难度模式：​​荣誉模式和自定义模式。荣誉模式是游戏的更难版本，为每个 Boss 战斗添加新动作，并使你无法保存渣滓（重新加载过去的保存以获得不同的结果）。甚至还有新的传奇动作，专门为让玩过该游戏的人措手不及而设计。 </p><figure id="attachment_3541104" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3541104" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3541104" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baldurs-Gate-3-Dark-Urge-Monk.jpg" alt="《博德之门 3》黑暗催动武僧（来源：Larian Studios）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baldurs-Gate-3-Dark-Urge-Monk.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baldurs-Gate-3-Dark-Urge-Monk-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baldurs-Gate-3-Dark-Urge-Monk-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baldurs-Gate-3-Dark-Urge-Monk-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baldurs-Gate-3-Dark-Urge-Monk-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baldurs-Gate-3-Dark-Urge-Monk-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3541104" class="wp-caption-text">鲍德尔的大门3黑暗敦促和尚（信用：拉里安·录音棚）</figcaption></figure><p>自定义模式正是锡在锡上听起来的样子，在游戏中增加了很多困难选择，以创建完美的玩法。</p><p>还有大量的修复程序，包括在游戏第3号法案中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-slowdown-issues-caused-by-crime-admits-developer-3550212">解决速度第3章的修复程序</a>，据报道，这是由于犯罪玩家的大量参与而引起的。</p><p>该补丁是30GB，需要安装130GB的可用空间，因此您需要在更新游戏之前在硬盘驱动器上腾出空间，或者可能会面临错误。</p><p> <em>NME</em>在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/baldurs-gate-3-review-3481761"><em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em>的五星级评论</a>中，将游戏称为“必不可少的幻想”，并补充说：“ <em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em>很乐意让您相信自己已经欺骗了它的系统，但是几乎没有它没有考虑到 - 您越涉及沉浸式幻想，富裕的拉里安（Larian）的胜利就变成了。”</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/heres-whats-coming-to-xbox-game-pass-in-december-3551394">Xbox Game Pass将在12月获得十二个新冠军，包括<em>《孤岛惊魂6》</em>和<em>《古墓丽影》的崛起</em>。</a></p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-gets-new-epilogue-and-new-difficulty-modes-in-30gb-update-3551420">“ Baldur&#39;s Gate 3”获得了新的结​​尾，而30GB更新中的新难度模式</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
